<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-7 bg-white mx-5 shadow border">
      <div class="row jam-info">
        <div class="col-9 border">

            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-12 py-2">
                <h3><%= @jam_session.title %></h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-4 border py-2">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                  <span class="fas fa-map-marker-alt mr-1"></span>
                  <span style="font-size: 14px;">
                    <%= @jam_session.location %>
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-4 border py-2">
                <div>
                  <span class="far fa-calendar-alt"></span>
                  <span><%= @jam_session.starts_at.strftime('%d %B') %></span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-4 border py-2">
                <div>
                  <span class="far fa-clock"></span>
                  <%= @jam_session.starts_at.strftime('%H:%M') %> -
                  <%= @jam_session.ends_at.strftime('%H:%M') %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>


            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12 py-2">
                <h5>Information</h5>
                <div class="py-2">
                  <%= @jam_session.description %>
                  Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Eaque officiis quaerat, aliquid, expedita ullam aliquam quisquam veniam eveniet aperiam ipsam vitae molestias amet ipsum similique dolor quia nisi id voluptate.
                </div>
                <p class="btn btn-primary btn-sm searchbtn">Join</p>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-3 border">
          <p>second</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row jam-map border">
        <div class="col-12 py-3">
          <div
            id="map"
            style="width: 100%;
            height: 280px;"
            data-markers="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
            data-mapbox-api-key="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>"
          ></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>





    <div class="col-4 bg-white shadow border">
      <p>Messages</p>
    </div>
  </div>





</div> <!-- end of container -->

